.Dd 
.Dt PAGESIZE 1
.Os BSD 4.2
.Sh NAME
.Nm pagesize
.Nd print system page size
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm pagesize
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm Pagesize
prints the size of a page of memory in bytes, as
returned by
.Xr getpagesize  2  .
This program is useful in constructing portable
shell scripts.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr getpagesize 2
.Sh HISTORY
.Nm Pagesize
appeared in 4.2 BSD.
